Description: SecuBox Domoticz - Home automation system
 Provides a web interface and API for managing Domoticz
 home automation system running in a container.
 .
 Features:
  - Container-based Domoticz deployment
  - Device and scene management
  - Hardware integration (Z-Wave, Zigbee, MQTT)
  - Backup and restore functionality
  - USB device passthrough support
